high_descs: Turn left to walk towards the bean bag. Make a right and then turn left to face the window, turning right again to go towards the chest of drawers.
Open the left top drawer and take out the tissue box inside it shut the drawer.
Turn right to face the bed and then to the left back towards the chest of drawers holding the box lower.
Place the tissue box on top of the chest of drawers on the CD.
anns.task_desc: To take out the tissue box to place it on top of drawers.

high_descs: Turn left, then turn right, to go around the bed and to the dresser to the left of the bed.
Open the top left drawer of the dresser.
Remove the tissue box from in the drawer.
Place the tissue box on top of the dresser, on the compact disk on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a tissue box on the dresser.
